description: For sale: $469,999. Due to MN Stay At Home Order, Seller requests no showings at this time.  Among the pine, birch, weeping willows & open country air, peace is found here!  This exquisite home has the best of one level living (incl in-floor radiant heat) w/a full bath & 2 add'l bdrms upstairs. Custom grey ship lap thru the main floor. Vaulted, two-story living w/accent windows & a gas fireplace. Bright, clean kitchen & dining area feat. an oversized walkout to the back patio. Spacious master suite is set apart from the rest of the home, w/walk-in closet & deluxe private bath.  Outside, is an abundant 25 acres to enjoy. The driveway winds from the quiet street, around the pond, past the superb 60x60 pole building & round horse pen, past the house & back to the horse barn.  Behind the house you'll find the back porch overlooking large backyard, pasture & into the woods. Prime location, perfect for those who need to be close to town, but want open spaces. See the photo captions for more details.

description: For sale: $299,900.

For sale: $419,900. Don't hold your horses, act now! You will want to put your brand on this purty little 18 acre spread! 36x60 Barn w/seven 12x12 stalls, a 12x12 tack room, plus a heckuvalot more, is ready for your horse to call home! This 3BR, 2BA home with geothermal heating/AC, offers a comfortable ambiance. Fresh paint in neutral tones bathe the walls & welcome all who gather here. The sunny kitchen w/new subway tile, double oven, gas cooktop, large walk-in pantry, & panoramic view out to the pasture, is sure to serve up plenty of smiles. Main floor laundry is handy  right off the garage. The living room begs for memorable family times and features beautiful hardwood floors. An updated full  bath & 2 nice sized bedrooms complete the upper level. The lower level master bedroom is a sanctuary of peace & relaxation complimented by a Franklin stove. You'll enjoy the heated floors in the master bath as well as the jetted tube & separate shower. See 3D tour & supplement for further house & barn details.

description: For sale: $310,000. Lovely modified two story in the desirable and established Goldenwood neighborhood. Landscaped front, patio pavers with a fire pit in the back of the home, retaining wall and a nice large deck allowing for great outdoor entertaining and relaxing. You will love the grand staircase that overlooks the two story living room with the beautiful gas fireplace that is the focal point with stone that goes all the way up the wall. This home has lots of natural light and is bright and neutral with many windows throughout. New kitchen appliances and fresh paint in the kitchen, dining room, master bedroom, bath, laundry and upper bedrooms and bath. Graciously sized master suite is on the main level and so is the laundry room off of the garage. Two generously sized bedrooms in the upper level with a full bathroom and the lower level is a wonderful open space with a bathroom rough-in and plenty of room to play, to watch TV, Game or to use as an exercise or hobby space. Make this your next home!
